BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:DJpjHuMvh72ehtDCTOMKo
SUMMARY:Twatties Open Mic of the Absurd!
DTSTAMP:20260405T040308Z
DTSTART:20260414T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Twatties! Seattle’s home to the zany and insane in C
	apitol Hill. We are an absurdist open mic variety show bringing old-Seattl
	e anti-normative joy. We offer performers four minutes to try anything in 
	front of a live and engaging audience. \n\nAll performance art such as sta
	ndup\, music\, poetry\, drag\, and puppets is welcomed. We showcase local 
	art installations\, a cozy atmosphere\, and great food and drink specials 
